"'''Rebel Jedi'''" is a miniadventure for the New Republic era, published on the [[Wizards of the Coast]] website. It was written by [[J.D. Wiker]] and published on [[October 23]], [[2003]]. It was followed by the miniadventure [[Nightsaber]].

==Publisher's summary==
Do the ends justify the means? In this Star Wars Roleplaying Game miniadventure, [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] himself sends the heroes to head off a rogue [[Jedi Praxeum|Jedi Academy]] student who plans to end the war with the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Empire]] -- by assassinating the [[Moff/Legends|Moffs]]! Can the heroes catch him? More importantly, will they stop him?

"Rebel Jedi" is a Star Wars Roleplaying Game miniadventure for four heroes of 15th level. It's set about [[12 ABY/Legends|12]] years after the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]]. The heroes are contacted by [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] Luke Skywalker to help him locate a Jedi student who has disappeared -- and may possibly have gone over to the [[Dark side of the Force/Legends|dark side]].

